  <section id="eip-818"><title>Element of Economics</title><para id="eip-472"><title>Trade promotes economic progress.</title></para></section><section id="eip-995"><title>Video</title><para id="eip-721"><figure id="moonlanding-youtube"><media id="yt-media" display="block" alt="Video of the Neil Armstrong on the Moon">
